caption.text:
Ta-da! The Game Interface assignment is finally done! I had fun doing this project!
The game is a stealth, 3rd person shooting game and the interface was mostly inspired by Batman : Arkham Asylum and Invisible Inc.
The cover was also heavily inspired by the picture of Batman looking over the Gotham City, if anything else on my pictures are similar to another game that I didn't state, then its PURELY coincidental. I have little knowledge of stealth game and I barely played one, so it was a huge challenge for me to make this!
Doing this assignment made me really really want to make games or participate in the project of game making :)
